summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of North & West Seventieth Street, from Greenwood Avenue to Eighth Avenue N.W. et al in the City of Seattle, by grading & curbing under Ordinance No. 17971, creating Local Improvement District No. 1699 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
